videos.headline: Houston gets ready with 'Cage Sway'
videos.description: The Cougars perform their pregame ritual along with the student section before taking on Rice.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Misc (Houston gets ready with 'Cage Sway') 2017/0916 OnScene Shortstop

videos.headline: Houston's Allen burst into end zone for TD
videos.description: Kyle Allen breaks several tackles to hustle his way into the end zone to score for the Cougars.

videos.headline: Houston DL Turner intercepts Rice's pass.
videos.description: Houston's Payton Turner tips the pass and makes impressive interception.

videos.headline: Cougars break through into end zone for a TD
videos.description: Dillion Birden runs straight into end zone for for 1-yard touchdown adding to Houston's lead.

videos.headline: Rice's QB Glaesmann commits his third turnover
videos.description: Houston's Ed Oliver forces fumble on  Sam Glaesmann  for another turnover.

videos.headline: Cougars' Leday jukes his way into the end zone
videos.description: Kyle Allen connects with John Leday for a 7-yard touchdown. to extend Houston's lead.
